<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Let=E2=80=99s say you want to make an animated=
 web series about cats. Not just any cats, though: The exciting twist in th=
is series is that these cats smoke marijuana.<a class=3D"footnote-index" hr=
ef=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importan=
t; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-st=
yle: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: in=
line-block;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a>=C2=A0You care a lot about this idea, and you want the production to be=
 perfect. You want to hire an amazing cast; you want celebrities like, <a h=
ref=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32699780.289424/aHR0cH=
M6Ly93d3cuaW1kYi5jb20vdGl0bGUvdHQxNTEzOTUxNi9mdWxsY3JlZGl0cz9yZWZfPXR0X292X=
3N0X3Nt/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB4b761ab2" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> I swear I am not making=
 this up</a>, Ashton Kutcher, Mila Kunis, Seth MacFarlane, Jane Fonda,=C2=
=A0Chris Rock and, of course, Vitalik Buterin (as Lord Catsington). That ta=
kes money.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">To raise the money, you go out to investors on=
 the internet and say =E2=80=9Chey, this series is gonna be amazing, I=E2=
=80=99ve got a great team and relationships with big celebrities, we=E2=80=
=99re gonna do sequels for ages, get in on the ground floor of a new entert=
ainment franchise that is basically the next Marvel or whatever, but with c=
ats who enjoy marijuana.=E2=80=9D And then you sell shares in the productio=
n, entitling investors to a share of the money you make. You sell these sha=
res=C2=A0on the internet, to anyone who shows up, without bothering to chec=
k if they are =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
lick/32699780.289424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbG=
VzLzIwMTgtMDktMjQvZWFybmluZy10aGUtcmlnaHQtdG8tZ2V0LXN3aW5kbGVkP2NtcGlkPUJCR=
