t=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked about this issue before</a>. The SE=
C very much takes the view that this sort of thing is a securities offering=
, and last month it <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/clic=
k/32699780.289424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9uZXdzL3ByZXNzLXJlbGVhc2UvMjAyM=
